# Dataset format and distribution
# ----------------
#
# The dataset is divided into three files: train / test and validation splits. 

3418 (19,652) train.jsonl (Projected using NMT)
1904 (10,791) val.jsonl (Projected using NMT)
1086 (5,633) test.jsonl (Manual)

*sizes in sentences (tokens)*


# Each token has the following notation: 
# a label on BIO scheme among these possible tags: 	

alarm/cancel_alarm
alarm/modify_alarm
alarm/set_alarm
alarm/show_alarms
alarm/snooze_alarm
alarm/time_left_on_alarm
reminder/cancel_reminder
reminder/set_reminder
reminder/show_reminders
weather/checkSunrise
weather/checkSunset
weather/find


# Dataset distribution is as follows:

val.jsonl
    162 alarm/cancel_alarm
     18 alarm/modify_alarm
    363 alarm/set_alarm
     77 alarm/show_alarms
     26 alarm/snooze_alarm
     20 alarm/time_left_on_alarm
    111 reminder/cancel_reminder
    420 reminder/set_reminder
    105 reminder/show_reminders
      2 weather/checkSunset
    600 weather/find
test.jsonl
    100 alarm/cancel_alarm
    100 alarm/modify_alarm
    100 alarm/set_alarm
     99 alarm/show_alarms
    100 alarm/snooze_alarm
    100 alarm/time_left_on_alarm
    100 reminder/cancel_reminder
    100 reminder/set_reminder
    100 reminder/show_reminders
     34 weather/checkSunrise
     54 weather/checkSunset
    100 weather/find
train.jsonl
    303 alarm/cancel_alarm
     45 alarm/modify_alarm
    578 alarm/set_alarm
    136 alarm/show_alarms
     52 alarm/snooze_alarm
     38 alarm/time_left_on_alarm
    224 reminder/cancel_reminder
    738 reminder/set_reminder
    202 reminder/show_reminders
      2 weather/checkSunrise
      3 weather/checkSunset
   1097 weather/find

